Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西怪怪的  我不知为啥有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为啥我正看着一点关系都没有的同县选手的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又不知为啥觉得差不多春日要搞点事出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  电话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  你今天很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两点整全员在车站前集合  老老实实地过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连一句话都没说上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘跟你说带东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一套泳装  还有足够的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…骑自行车过去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是啊  你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到的话  要请客的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.61,0:01:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才为什么会说出自行车的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一球能上垒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣…放哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就这样缴枪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  阿虚！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也才刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  多拿出点干劲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  全都到齐了  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去市民游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这准备的架势来看也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:18.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}夏天要有夏天的样子  不能不做有夏天特色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的时间可是一去不返的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在就要行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个只有一次的高一的暑假里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说阿虚  你有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便我们是用自行车去泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你们的自行车停哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  自行车只有你和我的两辆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？那个  也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 阿虚 可不能输给古泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  出发…立即！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼！罗刹！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  阿虚  接下来是要玩啊你怎么就筋疲力尽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的错啊  谁的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这人群  这消毒液的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真给人一种实在的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  赶快把行李放在一边占上地方去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就看不见那些禁止跳水的文字说明么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水温温的很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠  有希
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还站着干什么  快点过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙  不理她的话又该吵个不停了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那么  凉宫同学  请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…等…不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  还真让人感到和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我说的是凉宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得她也学会了有常识性的娱乐方法了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打个电话过来  单方面地说有事就挂的邀请方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在不能说得上是常识性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:05:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那点事  要我说根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得那么开心的凉宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会做什么震动这个世界的事情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  大概是我的错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春以来发生了种种事情的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得有点神经质了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙也是么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是市民泳池  倒应该是平民泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙  原来在那边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  她一个人在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？是啥  这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得这种景象以前也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前好像也见过这样的长门…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说起来  之后她似乎便会说出这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个就是我的团员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么他们都会听的  所以随便…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…吩咐他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩水中足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都要参加哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我难道具有预知能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你  阿虚  皮球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好像也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  偶然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常有的事了  既视感什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考虑了下今后的活动计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩余不多的暑假该如何度过的预定表啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在不到两周内搞完这个么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:53.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}要在不到两周内搞完这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠  有什么想要做的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我想捞金鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  捞金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天开始实行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近什么地方有盂兰盆会么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有烟花汇演也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头再联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了捞金鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是实玖瑠的强烈要求哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,付钱的又是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晚的要请客我不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  今天就此解散  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…我什么事也没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近如何  精神好么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么  那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  仅此而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  叫住了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  为什么我会去搭腔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天早晨  春日的电话又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说找到盂兰盆会的会场了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是今晚在市民运动场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢…唔哦哦哦哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  都非常合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦  是我给挑选的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我挑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐…赞  真赞！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…关键的东西在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  总觉得最近好像来过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个楼塔  那个店铺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有看过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  那边你想要玩的捞金鱼也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捞个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉…凉宫同学  请等一下～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个来  长门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对那种东西有兴趣么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  800日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为啥有种受她照顾的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西由我来买就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三条
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们不需要那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我和实玖瑠就一人拿了一条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  只吃一个的话没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有希  你那面具哪里弄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  接下来玩烟花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是夏天  在暑假中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  虽然极力想要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有件事情却让我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是捉昆虫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日啊  虽说玩也没问题  你暑假作业做完了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业？那种东西三天不就全部做完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种麻烦事就得事先赶紧收拾掉再玩到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是正确的享受暑假的方法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天真是太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  明天去捉昆虫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只能捉蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS团内捉蝉大战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  是个让人有种「连这也是啊」的感觉的大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS团内捉蝉大战就在这天开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说大家都努力奋斗过了  可应该说不出所料还是说啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获胜者是春日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然捕捉再放生的精神还是要有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放它们一条生路  以后说不定会来报恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想向余命无多的蝉要些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点像打开了盒子的潘多拉的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  不知为啥我们在一无所知的情况下  被套上了青蛙的罩衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在超市的门口做发气球的兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可算是理解除去装甲的Virtue的心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这待遇差算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长大叔也谢谢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要大叔的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很早之前就很想要这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也看在实玖瑠的份上说送给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就为了这种东西累死累活地干活么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把它放在社团室做纪念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠  你想什么时候穿都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个…十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上  夺去了我的安眠的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:12:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了不好的事情…这样下去我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会跟朝比奈学姐在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有点情况啊  你能现在能过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就去  马上就去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未  未…未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回不了未来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  事情是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在永久地重复着同样的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你满面春光地把那种非现实的话说出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道  没有比现在更清楚的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才和朝比奈学姐谈了下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是叫上我啊  这么美的谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后意识到最近这里时间的流动出现了异常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该说是朝比奈学姐的功绩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托她的福我也确信了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确信什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们似乎已经重复体验同样的时间许多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个刚才就听你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确地说应该是八月十七日到三十一日之间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正处于一个没有尽头的暑假的正当中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在确实是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绝对无法结束的Endless Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:15:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个世界里  九月一日之后的时间全部消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐无法回到未来也是因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是理所当然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物理性的没有未来哪里理所当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要谁相信那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望至少你能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们被困在那个叫什么封闭空间里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  并不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一部分的时间被分割开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到八月三十一日二十四时整的那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都被重置  再回到十七日的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是关于时间这个那个了的问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然未来人也混进来了  那我觉得也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这件事和朝比奈学姐没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原因是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凉宫同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然本人没有这个自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心里什么地方总在想着暑假不要结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啥啊  难道留着什么遗憾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许她是想着暑假还有什么事情剩下没做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了这个的话  问题就能迎刃而解了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像乐在其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最近频繁发生的既视感之谜终于解开了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  莫非全世界的人都感觉得到这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你算是特例了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只有和凉宫同学亲近的人才能感觉到这份异样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那春日怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙多少有一点意识到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说有了反而糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  别说是既视感了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得应该有一个人保存着所有轮回中的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话可真让人没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊  那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说也该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是超越了时空的情报统合思念体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得也许是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门  是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你全都记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带问下  这重复…现在到底几次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是第15513次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15513？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15513是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门  你在说啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那话是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么多的次数  我们全都在重复同样的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非全部如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15513次中没有去盂兰盆会的模式  有第2391次和第11054次的这两次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  去了盂兰盆会而没有捞金鱼的模式有437次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打工的有9031次  其内容有6个不同的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了发放气球  还有搬货物  收银  发送传单  接电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不  已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第15513次…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门她这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上两周的话就是…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是594年的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么长的时间仅她一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够好好地保留着记忆  无数次无数次地重复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门  你到底到现在为止都是什么样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不希望它存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是在地下的生活着的害羞人种
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是一群很友好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我看够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来找UFO吧  UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙到底想做啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个能搞清楚的话  问题也就迎刃而解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  试下这样怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从后面突然抱住凉宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她耳边轻语「I love you」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这由谁来做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你以外  有没有适合的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝权发动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说不干
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我来做怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的了  我做这角色还不够格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样只会让凉宫同学增加多余的混乱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  长门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在朝比奈学姐说出来之前  就注意到了这轮回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的任务是观察
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！快看  本垒打哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在活动来活动去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也去了真正的烟花汇演
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还去了钓虾虎鱼大会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外还有试胆  海水浴  保龄球  卡拉OK  电影连看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我觉得春日应该不会这样就满足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即便如此也没有什么行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  只有暑假剩余的日子是确实在一天天减少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后终于来到了  八月三十日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样课题就如实地完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就这样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  各位  还有什么想做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个暑假已经做了好多事了  已经很充实了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该还没有满足才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天当预备日先空下来了  大家就这样休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天在社团教室再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊  春日！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  如果你就这样回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这样回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那重复了一万几千次的两星期又要陷入永远循环的窘境了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我该做什么呢  应该说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在春日的话里  应该有提示的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.43,0:22:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她至今都说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…春日！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.55,0:22:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.77,0:23:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月三十一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业  还没动过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢  怎么都成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.05,0:23:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再重复的话  作业做了也没意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管明天来不来  到时候就交给那时的我算啦


